Package adept.module

Provides interfaces and classes to support DEFT TA1 algorithm implementations in the ADEPT framework, primarily based on the AbstractModule class along with a set of Processor interfaces, which together support specific subclasses for analysis, extraction, tagging and other algorithms.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IChunkProcessor<T extends HltContent> The Interface IChunkProcessor defines the interfaces that will be implemented by ADEPT modules that perform chunk-level processing and return as output HLT content.
IConversationProcessor The IConversationProcessor Interface defines the interfaces that will be implemented by ADEPT modules that process CUBISM Conversation objects..
IDocumentHltContentProcessor<T extends HltContent> The Interface IDocumentHltContentProcessor defines the interfaces that will be implemented by ADEPT modules that process a Document for HL content extraction and need additional (or previously extracted) HLT metadata of specific HltContent type to produce as output one or more HltContent objects of that type.
IDocumentListProcessor The Interface IDocumentListProcessor defines the interfaces that will be implemented by ADEPT modules that process list of Documents and returns HltContentContainer object containing one or more objects of HltContent type.
IDocumentProcessor The Interface IDocumentProcessor defines the interfaces that will be implemented by ADEPT modules that for HL content extraction and need additional (or previously extracted) HLT metadata available in HltContentContainer to output an augmented or new HltContentContainer containing one or more objects of HltContent type.
IModule The Interface IModule defines the interfaces that are generic across all the ADEPT algorithm modules.
IPassagePairProcessor<T extends HltContent> The Interface IPassagePairProcessor defines the interfaces that will be implemented by ADEPT modules that perform processing on pair of passages.
IPassageProcessor<T extends HltContent> The Interface IPassageProcessor defines the interfaces that will be implemented by ADEPT modules that perform passage-level processing and return as output HLT content.
ISentencePairProcessor<T extends HltContent> The Interface ISentencePairProcessor defines the interfaces that will be implemented by ADEPT modules that perform processing on pair of sentences.
ISentenceProcessor<T extends HltContent> The Interface ISentenceProcessor defines the interfaces that will be implemented by ADEPT modules that perform sentence-level processing. .

Package adept.module Description

Provides interfaces and classes to support DEFT TA1 algorithm implementations in the ADEPT framework, primarily based on the AbstractModule class along with a set of Processor interfaces, which together support specific subclasses for analysis, extraction, tagging and other algorithms.
